dc_description_s: This data layer represents municipalities for Taylor County, Wisconsin in 2013. It is a feature class within the geodatabase “Taylor_Municipalities_2013.gdb”. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are “Taylor_Municipalities_2013” and “Unincorporated_Villages”. [This dataset contains the current municipal boundaries based up existing parcel data. Previously, Taylor County had separate datasets for townships and cities/villages. As updates are made to parcels or as boundary lines change this dataset will need to also be updated.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison.
